Litecoin was just released, it was added to some of the exchange services and its price went up so fast, no one expected. The speed of transactions, the already built-in SegWit, and the larger reward for mining indicate bright prospects for the LTC price. Litecoin price could possibly be a rival for the Ethereum in 2019.</p>\n<p>When you looking for Litecoin news there you can find the experts predict a potential convergence of ETH and LTC prices courses notwithstanding the ETH overtakes LTC at a cost of more than 5 times. A number of crypto enthusiasts suggest that the difference in ETH and LTC prices in 2019 will be no more than 3 times. Perspectives for the further development of LTC are based on the following characteristics of the coin:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>High transaction speed;</li>\n<li>A built-in protocol that increases the plasticity of the system and the speed of operations;</li>\n<li>A large amount of reward for cloud mining.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"market-prediction-2019\">Market prediction for Litecoin (LTC) price 2019</h3>\n<p>Sam Quinn, the author of the online publication with a focus on Ethereum analysis, said that he didn\'t believe in serious competition between LTC and ETH. Mr. Quinn calls the state in which the crypto sphere is located is \"infancy\". He draws an analogy with children\'s cries – when \"baby\" cries louder, that attracts the primary attention.</p>\n<p>Litecoin is still a quieter \"child\", but it has a chance to start early rapid growth. For this reason, LTC price in 2019 can behave unpredictably. In addition, in the last couple of years, the crypto has behaved positively, except for the depreciation of the course in January 2018.</p>\n<p>Also, around the Litecoin news were versions of the price of Litecoin for 2019 in the range of 350-500 USD for 1 LTC. However, there are those who predict the loss of Litecoin popularity, which ultimately will lead to a fall in Litecoin volume and finally drop the Litecoin price for this reason.</p>\n<p>The Economic Forecasting Agency analyzes not only real money but also cryptocurrencies. Specialists in this company suggest that there should be no surprising jumps in the Litecoin price in 2019. Moreover, the LTC price will fluctuate throughout the year, constantly rising and falling.</p>\n<h3 id=\"verdict\">Litecoin price prediction verdict</h3>\n<p>Litecoin price grew in 2013, then fell down, and then in 2017 started to grow again with the high speed, so LTC is one of “unexpected” cryptos. Some experts hypothesize that the popularity of this coin will come to naught, which in turn will lead to the collapse of the Litecoin price and the exit of Litecoin from the market. But despite all the arguments against of Litecoin, its price may be between $ 200-400, because LTC price still didn’t reach $ 80-100 and could possibly grow up in 2019.</p>\n<h3>How to choose Litecoin (LTC) wallet</h3>\n<div class=\"item-page-image-template\">\n<div class=\"item-page-blog-image\"><img src=\"https://atomicwallet.io/css/images/mainnotebook.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n<p>To store your funds you need to have <a href=\"https://atomicwallet.io/litecoin\">non-custodial Litecoin wallet</a> Atomic Wallet it\'s just such a wallet, your Private keys are stored on your device and never leave it, so you money is totally under your control. Atomic is a universal wallet with 300+ cryptocurrency assets, built-in exchange and “Buy crypto” service, so you’ll got all you need in one secure interface.</p>\n<h3>How to exchange Litecoin (LTC)</h3>\n<p>Atomic Wallet allows you to exchange cryptocurrency using a built-in instant exchange between more than 60 assets at the best available rate via Changelly, ChangeNOW or Shapeshift.</p>\n<div class=\"item-page-image-template mobile-hide\">\n<div class=\"item-page-blog-image\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rpPqCCFZuHs\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n<h3>How to buy Litecoin (LTC)</h3>\n<p>The most legal way to buy Litecoin is to buy it with a credit card, but usually it takes some time to process the bank data and proceed the transaction. In Atomic Wallet you can buy Litecoin with a credit card and get it already in a 30 minutes – it’s the most fast and legal way to buy cryptocurrency with VISA or MasterCard.</p>\n<div class=\"item-page-image-template mobile-hide\">\n<div class=\"item-page-blog-image\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ANVwv89vR5E\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n<p><cite>The arcticle has an informative purpose. The Atomic Wallet team is not trying to persuade or endorse you, neither are we making warranties for the accuracy of the content. All decisions are made at your own risk.</cite></p>'),(999,314,'_bottom_content_block','field_5cf10ebb9ad86'),(1000,314,'button_suggest_left_text','How Atomic Works?'),(1001,314,'_button_suggest_left_text','field_5cf1128c011cc'),(1002,314,'button_suggest_left_link','#'),(1003,314,'_button_suggest_left_link','field_5cf112d8011cd'),(1004,314,'button_suggest_right_text','How your keys stored in Atomic?'),(1005,314,'_button_suggest_right_text','field_5cf112e6011ce'),(1006,314,'button_suggest_right_link','#'),(1007,314,'_button_suggest_right_link','field_5cf112ee011cf'),(1008,263,'_edit_lock','1560773060:1'),(1009,315,'_wp_attached_file','2019/05/buy-bitcoin-2.png'),(1010,315,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1052;s:6:\"height\";i:812;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2019/05/buy-bitcoin-2.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"buy-bitcoin-2-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"buy-bitcoin-2-300x232.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:232;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\