nd USD. On the XRP Ledger, such a transaction costs $0.00001, and this amount is non-replenishable, i.e. with every single transaction made via the XRP Ledger, the world loses $0.00001. For that reason, spamming becomes senseless.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>XRP is one of the fastest and more scalable blockchains on the market nowadays that can become a competitor to the Visa or Mastercard when comparing to the TPS (transactions per second).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>XRP runs a consensus of network validator which allows to handle over 1,500 transactions per second. The consensus enables applications to get relevant information on the content state by sharing a worldwide ledger which is generated a few times in a minute. Once accepted and validated, the content gets encrypted in a ledger and never changes. The whole sequence of validated ledgers is called the ledger history.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ripple XRP Wallet</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Atomic Wallet provides you one of the best options to store, send, exchange and buy XRP.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://support.atomicwallet.io/support/solutions/articles/36000066351-how-to-install-atomic-wallet-/preview&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1542036001633000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGA_-1shdjA3oLOOgArJI3fzcvfkQ\">Install</a>&nbsp;Ripple wallet and mange XRP right in the Atomic Interface.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Don\'t forget that to manage your XRP in Atomic, you\'ll need to have at least 20 XRP as an unspendable balance to make a transaction successful. This measure is needed to use a personal XRP wallet address in the XRP Ledger. Learn more about this feature and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://atomicwallet.io/what-is-destination-tag\">XRP destination tags</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Takeaways</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\